{{Starbox catalog
|names=参宿四，[[拜耳命名法|α Ori]]，[[佛氏命名法|58 Ori]]，[[Harvard_Revised_catalogue|HR]] 2061, [[Bonner_Durchmusterung|BD]] +7° 1055, [[Henry_Draper_Catalogue|HD]] 39801, [[Catalogues_of_Fundamental_Stars|FK5]] 224, [[Hipparcos_catalogue|HIP]] 27989, [[Smithsonian_Astrophysical_Observatory_Star_Catalog|SAO]] 113271, [[Boss_General_Catalogue|GC]] 7451, [[Catalog_of_Components_of_Double_and_Multiple_Stars|CCDM]] J05552+0724AP, [[American_Association_of_Variable_Star_Observers|AAVSO]] 0549+07
